<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha"><g ref="sym:tam-pillaiyarCuli" type="punctuation"> <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> </g> svasti śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> tribhuvanaccakravartti</hi>kaḷ maturaiyuṅ koṇṭu pāṇṭiyaṉ muṭit talaiyum Īḻamuṅ koṇṭaruḷiya <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>kulottuṅkacoḻa<hi rend="grantha">de</hi>vaṟku yāṇṭu <num value="18"><g type="numeral">10</g> 8</num> Āvatu
<lb n="2"/><hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>yaṅkoṇṭacoḻamaṇṭalattuk kāliyūrkkoṭṭattu taniyūr <hi rend="grantha">śrīrājendra</hi>coḻa- <hi rend="grantha"><unclear>cca</unclear></hi>tu<hi rend="grantha">rvvedimaṅgala</hi>ttu Uṭaiyār tiruppulivalamuṭaiyāṟku Immaṇṭalattuk kaḷat
<lb n="3" break="no"/>tūrkkoṭṭattu Aiñ<unclear>cūr</unclear> mullaipāṭit tiruccurakkaṇṇappaṉ Ātiṉāyakaṉ pañca<unclear>na</unclear>tivāṇaṉāṉa Irā[<hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>*]rā[<hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>*] nilakaṅkaraiyaṉ vaitta rununtitāviḷakku Oṉṟukku viṭṭa
<lb n="4"/>pacu <num value="32">3 <g type="numeral">10</g> 2</num>- m <hi rend="grantha">ṛṣabha</hi>m 1- m Ippacu muppattiraṇṭum <hi rend="grantha">vṛṣabha</hi>m Oṉṟum Iṉṉāyaṉār koyilil tirununtāviḷakkuk kuṭimakkaḷil maṉṟāṭi peruṅkāṭaṉ makaṉ Uṭai
<lb n="5" break="no"/>yāṉkoṉ viḷakku Araiyum nampi makaṉ Irācakkoṉ viḷakku kālum piṭāraṉ makaṉ ceṅkāṭakkoṉ viḷakku kālum Āka viḷakku Oṉṟukku Ippacu muppa
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ttira<unclear>ṇṭu</unclear>m <hi rend="grantha">vṛṣabha</hi>mum kaikkoṇṭu cela<unclear>vu</unclear> rā<hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>ke<hi rend="grantha">sa</hi>riyāle ni<hi rend="grantha">tya</hi>m Uḻakku ney <hi rend="grantha">candrāditya</hi>varai celuttakkaṭavomāka <hi rend="grantha">sa</hi>mmatittuccilālekai <unclear>pa</unclear><note n="156-1">A few letters are omitted to be engraved at the end.</note>
</p>

